rvices or restrict your access to parts or all of the Site without notice or liability. MakerStorage, LLC  may terminate your use of the Site at any time in its sole discretion.</p>","<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">These terms apply exclusively to your access to and use of the Site and do not alter the terms or conditions of any other agreement you may have with MakerStorage, LLC, its subsidiaries, or affiliates.</p>","","<ol>"," \t<li><strong>Privacy.</strong></li>","</ol>","<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">You acknowledge and agree that MakerStorage, LLC  may use the data collected in the course of our relationship for its private use.</p>","","<ol start=\"2\">"," \t<li><strong>Electronic Communications.</strong></li>","</ol>","<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">When you visit the MakerStorage, LLC  Site or send e-mails to us, you are communicating with us electronically. You consent to receive communications from us electronically. We will communicate with you by e-mail or by posting notices on the MakerStorage, LLC  Site. You agree that all agreements, notices, disclosures and other communications that we provide to you electronically satisfy any legal requirement that such communications be in writing.</p>","","<ol start=\"3\">"," \t<li><strong>Intellectual Property.</strong></li>","</ol>","<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">3.1. Trademarks. “MakerStorage”, and other MakerStorage graphics, logos, trade names, and service names are trademarks, of MakerStorage, LLC  in the U.S. and/or other countries. MakerStorage, LLC’s trademarks and trade dress may not be used in connection with any product or service that is not MakerStorage, LLC ’s, in any manner that is likely to cause confusion among customers, or in any manner that disparages or discredits MakerStorage, LLC. All other trademarks not owned by MakerStorage, LLC  that appear on this Site are the property of their respective owners, who may or may not be affiliated with, connected to, or sponsored by MakerStorage, LLC.</p>","<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">3.2. Patents. One or more patents or patents pending owned by MakerStorage, LLC or its affiliates may apply to the MakerStorage, LLC  Site and to the features, products, and services accessible via the MakerStorage, LLC  Site. Portions of the MakerStorage, LLC  Site may operate under license of one or more patents.</p>","","<ol start=\"4\">"," \t<li><strong>License and Site Access.</strong></li>","</ol>","<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">4.1. License and limitations. MakerStorage, LLC  grants you a limited license to access and make personal use of the MakerStorage, LLC  Site. You may not to download (other than page caching) or modify it, or any portion of it, except with express written consent of MakerStorage, LLC . This license does not include any resale or commercial use of the MakerStorage, LLC  or its contents; any derivative use of the MakerStorage, LLC  Site or its contents; any downloading or copying of account information; or any use of data mining, robots, or similar data gathering and extraction tools. Unless otherwise specified by MakerStorage, LLC  in a separate license, your right to use any software, data, documentation or other materials that you access or download through the MakerStorage, LLC  Site is subject to these Terms.</p>","<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The MakerStorage, LLC  Site or any portion of the MakerStorage, LLC  Site may not be reproduced, duplicated, copied, sold, resold, visited, or otherwise exploited for any commercial purpose without express written consent of MakerStorage, LLC. You may not frame or utilize framing techniques to enclose any trademark, logo, or other proprietary information (including images, text, page layout, or form) of MakerStorage, LLC without express written consent. You may not use any meta tags or any other “hidden text” utilizing MakerStorage, LLC’s name or trademarks without the express written consent of MakerStorage, LLC. Any unauthorized use terminates the permission or license granted by MakerStorage, LLC.</p>","<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">4.2. Link Creation. You are granted a limited, revocable, and nonexclusive right to create a hyperlink to the home page of the MakerStorage, LLC Site, so long as the link does not portray MakerStorage, LLC, or its products or services in a false, misleading, derogatory, or otherwise offensive matter. You may not use any MakerStorage, LLC logo or other proprietary graphic or trademark as part of the link without express written permission.</p>","","<ol start=\"5\">"," \t<li><strong>Disclaimers and Limitations of Liability.</strong></li>","</ol>","<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">THE MAKERSTORAGE, LLC  SITE AND ALL INFORMATION, CONTENT, MATERIALS, PRODUCTS (INCLUDING ANY SOFTWARE) AND SERVICES INCLUDED ON OR OTHERWISE MADE AVAILABLE TO YOU THROUGH THIS SITE ARE PROVIDED BY MAKERSTORAGE, LLC  ON AN “AS IS” AND “AS AVAILABLE” BASIS, UNLESS OTHERWISE SPECIFIED IN THE AGREEMENT. MAKERSTORAGE, LLC  MAKES NO REPRESENTATIONS OR WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, AS TO THE OPERATION OF THIS SITE OR THE INFORMATION, CONTENT, MATERIALS, PRODUCTS (INCLUDING ANY SOFTWARE) OR SERVICES INCLUDED ON OR OTHERWISE MADE AVAILABLE TO YOU THROUGH THE MAKERSTORAGE, LLC SITE, UNLESS OTHERWISE SPECIFIED IN WRITING. YOU EXPRESSLY AGREE THAT YOUR USE OF THIS SITE IS AT YOUR SOLE RISK. TO THE FULL EXTENT PERMISSIBLE BY APPLICABLE LAW, MAKERSTORAGE, LLC DISCLAIMS ALL WARRANTIES, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING, BUT NOT LIMITED TO, IMPLIED WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY AND FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE. MAKERSTORAGE, LLC DOES NOT WARRANT THAT THIS SITE; INFORMATION, CONTENT, MATERIALS, PRODUCTS (INCLUDING ANY SOFTWARE) OR SERVICES INCLUDED ON OR OTHERWISE MADE AVAILABLE TO YOU THROUGH THE MAKERSTORAGE, LLC SITE; ITS SERVERS; OR E-MAIL SENT FROM MAKERSTORAGE, LLC ARE FREE OF VIRUSES OR OTHER HARMFUL COMPONENTS. MAKERSTORAGE, LLC WILL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY DAMAGES OF ANY KIND ARISING FROM THE USE OF THE MAKERSTORAGE, LLC SITE OR FROM ANY INFORMATION, CONTENT, MATERIALS, PRODUCTS (INCLUDING SOFTWARE) OR SERVICES INCLUDED ON OR OTHERWISE MADE AVAILABLE TO YOU THROUGH THE MAKERSTORAGE, LLC SITE, INCLUDING, BUT NOT LIMITED TO DIRECT, INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, PUNITIVE, AND CONSEQUENTIAL DAMAGES, UNLESS OTHERWISE SPECIFIED IN THE AGREEMENT. CERTAIN STATE LAWS DO NOT ALLOW LIMITATIONS ON IMPLIED WARRANTIES OR THE EXCLUSION OR LIMITATION OF CERTAIN DAMAGES. IF THESE LAWS APPLY TO YOU, SOME OR ALL OF THE ABOVE DISCLAIMERS, EXCLUSIONS, OR LIMITATIONS MAY NOT APPLY TO YOU, AND YOU MIGHT HAVE ADDITIONAL RIGHTS.</p>","","<ol start=\"6\">"," \t<li><strong>Governing Law.</strong></li>","</ol>","<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">You agree that the laws of the state of Delaware, without regard to principles of conflict of laws, will govern these Site Terms and any dispute of any sort that might arise between you and MakerStorage LLC.</p>","","<ol start=\"7\">"," \t<li><strong>Venue.</strong></li>","</ol>","<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Any dispute relating in any way to these Terms will be adjudicated in a court of competent jurisdiction in Delaware. You consent to exclusive jurisdiction and venue in such courts. We may seek injunctive or other relief in any state, federal, or national court of competent jurisdiction for any actual or alleged infringement of our, our affiliates, or any third-party’s intellectual property or other proprietary rights.</p>","","<ol start=\"8\">"," \t<li><strong>Modification and Severability.</strong></li>","</ol>","<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">8.1. Modification. We reserve the right to make changes to the MakerStorage, LLC Site and these Terms at any time. The modified Terms will become effective upon posting on the MakerStorage, LLC Site or, if we notify you by email, as stated in the email message. By continuing to use the Site after the effective date of any modifications to this Agreement, you agree to be bound by the modified terms. It is your responsibility to check the MakerStorage, LLC Site regularly for modifications to these Terms.</p>","<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">8.2. Severability. If any portion of these Terms is held to be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining portions of these Terms will remain in full force and effect. Any invalid or unenforceable portions will be interpreted to effect and intent of the original portion. If such construction is not possible, the invalid or unenforceable portion will be severed from these Terms but the rest of these Terms will remain in full force and effect.</p>"]}],[{"start":{"row":13,"column":0},"end":{"row":13,"column":21},"action":"remove","lines":["<h1>Terms of Use</h1>"],"id":5}]]},"ace":{"folds":[],"scrolltop":0,"scrollleft":0,"selection":{"start":{"row":13,"column":0},"end":{"row":13,"column":0},"isBackwards":false},"options":{"guessTabSize":true,"useWrapMode":false,"wrapToView":true},"firstLineState":{"row":140,"mode":"ace/mode/php"}},"timestamp":1462648158112,"hash":"868191e139756585614af928f1cf8eae73962886"}